{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/862643192/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ssh的博客","author":"ssh"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"42ba3851-3b12-5637-b9dc-2564caae85a8","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>本文首发公众号「<a href=\"https://oscimg.oschina.net/oscnet/up-fa75de6c6ac2dbce9cb2e85b58753d4568b.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">前端从进阶到入院</a>」，欢迎关注！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012015_630e101a_1087321.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"近况\"><a href=\"#%E8%BF%91%E5%86%B5\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>近况</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012030_b8ea9e2f_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>158 万</strong>周活跃用户（通过 devtools 插件来统计），<strong>940 万</strong>的月下载量。</p>\n<h2 id=\"对比去年\"><a href=\"#%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>对比去年</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012151_cbf950ef_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>Devtools：110 万 -> 158 万（+43.6%） NPM：620 万 -> 940 万（+51.6%）</p>\n<h2 id=\"vue-30-one-piece\"><a href=\"#vue-30-one-piece\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vue 3.0 One Piece</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012242_a695cd67_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012303_70986902_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>自那之后，Vue3 逐渐趋于稳定，继续探索用户体验。</p>\n<h2 id=\"vue-router-40\"><a href=\"#vue-router-40\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vue Router 4.0</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012410_c150f18a_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>已经稳定。</p>\n<h2 id=\"vuex-40\"><a href=\"#vuex-40\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vuex 4.0</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012436_975c87ba_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>已经稳定。</p>\n<h2 id=\"生态\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%80%81\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>生态</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012507_3a502d58_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>慢慢赶上了！</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Nuxt 3</li>\n<li>Vuetify</li>\n<li>Quasar</li>\n<li>Element Plus</li>\n<li>Ant Design Vue</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"用户体验\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>用户体验</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012602_8eece2b0_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>持续探索中：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>新的构建工具</li>\n<li>更棒的语法</li>\n<li>IDE/TS 支持</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"构建工具\"><a href=\"#%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>构建工具</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/012817_2b34b042_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>Vite，不用说了，今年的明星项目。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>和 Vue-CLI 更加相似的体验</li>\n<li>基于 ESM 的 HMR 热更新</li>\n<li>ESBuild 提供依赖预构建</li>\n<li>Rollup 兼容的插件接口</li>\n<li>内置 SSR 支持</li>\n<li>更多更多……</li>\n</ul>\n<p>可以扩展阅读笔者之前写的<a href=\"https://juejin.cn/post/6932367804108800007\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">浅谈 Vite 2.0 原理，依赖预编译，插件机制是如何兼容 Rollup 的？</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/013328_a14d8061_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>Vite 还是 Vue-CLI？</p>\n<ul>\n<li>短期内会共存</li>\n<li>长期会融合：Vite 的速度 + Vue-CLI 的全面度支持</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"测试\"><a href=\"#%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>测试</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/013456_ee8f5725_1087321.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Cypress 新版组件测试</li>\n<li>@web/test-runner</li>\n<li>Jest 集成进行中</li>\n</ul>\n<p>看了下 <code class=\"language-text\">@web/test-runner</code> 的简介，非常全面的测试解决方案：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/013730_8ab1be13_1087321.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"vitepress\"><a href=\"#vitepress\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>VitePress</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/014112_43c3431a_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>基于 Vue3 + Vite 的静态站点生成器。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/014145_35ec8a41_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>它的独特之处在于：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>利用 SPA 的开发体验来定制用户主题</li>\n<li>在 Markdown 里自由加入动态组件</li>\n<li>自动消除静态内容的“双重负载”</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/015752_04714064_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>利用 VitePress 这个平台，探索未来 SSR/SSG 优化（Eat Your Own Dog Food）</p>\n<ul>\n<li>更积极的消除静态内容（甚至是主题组件）</li>\n<li>更高效的构建</li>\n<li>按需构建 + 边缘缓存</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"新的开发体验\"><a href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>新的开发体验</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/020121_3075f295_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>利用编译器做更多事情：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">script setup</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">style</code> CSS 变量注入</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"script-setup\"><a href=\"#script-setup\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>script setup</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/020154_4a152c1e_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/020209_8a1f98d5_1087321.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/rfcs/blob/script-setup-2/active-rfcs/0000-script-setup.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">RFC 地址</a></li>\n<li>在单文件组件中提供更符合用户体验的 Composition API</li>\n<li>提高运行时性能</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"style-变量注入\"><a href=\"#style-%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E6%B3%A8%E5%85%A5\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>style 变量注入</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/020339_ec39cc14_1087321.png\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/rfcs/blob/style-vars-2/active-rfcs/0000-sfc-style-variables.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">RFC 地址</a></li>\n<li>利用 <code class=\"language-text\">v-bind()</code> 在单文件组件的 <code class=\"language-text\">style</code> 中注入 JS 状态驱动的 CSS 变量</li>\n<li>CSS-in-JS 的好处尽享，但避免了它的心智负担。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"更好的-idets-支持\"><a href=\"#%E6%9B%B4%E5%A5%BD%E7%9A%84-idets-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>更好的 IDE/TS 支持</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/020519_813698a3_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>多个探索中的项目</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Vetur</li>\n<li>VueDX</li>\n<li>Volar</li>\n</ul>\n<p>获得了：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>类型检查，语法提示和 SFC templates 的自动重构</li>\n</ul>\n<p>接下来：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>把这些努力整合成更推荐的链路</strong></li>\n<li>提供 CLI 工具来利用 TS 校验 SFC</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/020759_6a709583_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>计划：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>基于 Volar 的<strong>新的官方 VSCode 插件</strong>，从 Vetur 和 VueDX 上汲取很多灵感。</li>\n<li>通过内部设计来支持其他编辑器，通过 LSP（Language Service Protocol）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"未来\"><a href=\"#%E6%9C%AA%E6%9D%A5\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>未来</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/020936_e3b1730e_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>我们在 Vue3 中放弃了 IE11。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/rfcs/blob/ie11/active-rfcs/0000-vue3-ie11-support.md\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">RFC</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/rfcs/discussions/296\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">讨论</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>笔者对这个 RFC 也进行了翻译：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3NTM5NDgzOA==&#x26;mid=2247495151&#x26;idx=1&#x26;sn=981920c2345fb3a70097b2a8dfa5ba66&#x26;chksm=eb07d596dc705c80b9db1bf62b0cc614b4f4012087e994ad178d5d91cfc3b9ad16f5c5ae72f0&#x26;token=1932513687&#x26;lang=zh_CN#rd\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Vue3 考虑彻底放弃 IE 浏览器</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/021110_2343bc4d_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>Vue 2.7 会成为坚持留守 IE11 人群的选择，它会提供更多的 Vue3 特性和 TS 支持。（估计在 2021 第三季度）</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/021245_168586dc_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>Vue3 的集成构建也要来了！</p>\n<ul>\n<li>估计在<strong>四月末</strong></li>\n<li>可单独配置来兼容 v2</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/021338_7e3fe333_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/021353_dddaff8e_1087321.png\"></p>\n<p>Vue3 会在 2021 二季度末尾，变成新的默认版本！</p>\n<ul>\n<li>npm 的 lastest tag 会默认安装 Vue3</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://vuejs.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">vuejs.org</a> 官网会指向 Vue3 的文档</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.gitee.com/uploads/images/2021/0415/021440_19fa2876_1087321.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"感谢大家\"><a href=\"#%E6%84%9F%E8%B0%A2%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>感谢大家</h2>\n<p>欢迎关注 ssh，前端潮流趋势、原创面试热点文章应有尽有。</p>\n<p>记得关注后加我好友，我会不定期分享前端知识，行业信息。2021 陪你一起度过。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://oscimg.oschina.net/oscnet/up-fa75de6c6ac2dbce9cb2e85b58753d4568b.png\"></p>","timeToRead":5,"frontmatter":{"title":"VueConf 2021 抢先看，Evan You 和你聊聊 Vue 的未来","date":"April 20, 2021","spoiler":""},"fields":{"slug":"/862643192/","langKey":"en"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/862643192/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/830777874/","langKey":"en","directoryName":"830777874"},"frontmatter":{"title":"打破 React Hook 必须按顺序、不能在条件语句中调用的枷锁"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/889568539/","langKey":"en","directoryName":"889568539"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[RFC] 关于 Vue 3 的 IE11 支持"}},"translations":[],"translatedLinks":[]}},"staticQueryHashes":["336482444"]}